:0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e6027b9c378daacf12d42bafe180fe99b6b6f9e","tid":2441352,"uid":370392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"呢套係神作<br />\n次次睇到最後都會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後係好感人<br />\n淒美，搵唔到再出發<br />\n但諗深一層，又係好美好嘅一生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"都係<br />\n覺得結局係咁<br />\n女主角因為愛情而顯得耀眼，過咗精彩嘅一生<br />\n呢啲一切都係畫家帶俾佢<br />\n<br />\n佢話鍾意咁發光發亮嘅自己嗰下好感觸<br />\n我都希望自己都可以好似女主角咁鍾意一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4756e8c6856111607d956b5563a1540a57bc605b","tid":2441352,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0aa5b3129f434247764e8aaf28823a92384a493","tid":2441352,"uid":255489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:11:20.000Z","msg":"今敏作品無論過左幾多年睇，都係好感人，引起人共鳴。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得佢好捉到人性<br />\n每部作品都用唔同方法， 講到人嘅本質"},{"pid":"51616c136b23e2e06b5a98828b77d1f4222f1114","tid":2441352,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88840bf532fd802cd7f573718794346a73d23f6d","tid":2441352,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:14:38.000Z","msg":"今敏點解咁早死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢啲戲最鐘意千年女優"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天妒英才<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4637d92ec233fe3d7a0a0567be8fd